'''Taluẓert d truẓert''' d sin n yirmawen yettusmerasen s tuget deg waṭas n tɣulin tussnanin yemgaraden am [[tasnudert|tesnudert]] d [[tasensartut|tsensartut]] i wakken ad mmelen tirwasin d yimgaraden n iylanen n isegran ama di [[tanga|tnegwa]] neɣ deg [[amuddir|imuddiren]] 

Qqaren ɣef tenga d akken-itt d taluẓert ma tella tsuddest-is neɣ aglam-is (am yini, talɣa, ableɣ, azuk...) d yiwen. Ma d tanga taruẓert d tin yemgaraden deg iylanen i d-ittwadren ya.

